Name: Docking
checklistText:
1. Index Bar - EXTEND
2. Exterior Lights - DOCK
3. (optional)Encoder CMD: 250, ACQ Lights OFF
4. (optional)Encoder CMD: 141, Approach Lights ON
5. (optional)Encoder CMD: 201, Agenda display BRIGHT
6. If Agena is not rigid, Encoder CMD: 221 - Rigidize

Keep docking port centered, zero IVI's until docking complete.
Warning: Keep alignment with target, keep speed low.
